<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>부곡중학교 3학년 영어 분석 | 영어쑥쑥어학원</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@400;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink:    #1C2B3A;
    --slate:  #3B5068;
    --steel:  #6B8299;
    --gold:   #C9A84C;
    --gold-lt:#F0E4C0;
    --cream:  #F7F4EE;
    --panel:  #EEF1F5;
    --rule:   #C5CDD8;
    --white:  #FFFFFF;

    --diff-high: #8C4A4A;
    --diff-mid:  #7A6830;
    --diff-low:  #3A6B50;
    --diff-high-bg: #F5ECEC;
    --diff-mid-bg:  #F5F2E8;
    --diff-low-bg:  #ECF2EE;

    --area-dialogue: #4A6FA5;
    --area-text:     #5C8A6E;
    --area-vocab:    #8E6FA3;
    --area-grammar:  #B07D52;
    --area-written:  #6A8FA0;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .site-header {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  }
  .site-header-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .logo { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .logo-main { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
  .logo-sub  { font-size: 10px; color: #7A9BB5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 300; }
  .header-badge {
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
    color: var(--gold);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1E2E 0%, var(--slate) 100%);
    padding: 52px 24px 44px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -40px; left: 30%;
    width: 180px; height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
  }
  .hero-title span { color: var(--gold); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #8BAFC8;
    font-weight: 300;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  .hero-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
  }
  .hero-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    min-width: 110px;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .hero-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
  .hero-card-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--white); display: block; }
  .hero-card-val.gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .hero-card-lab { font-size: 10px; color: #8BAFC8; margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 300; }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }

  /* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
  .sec-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 52px;
  }
  .sec-head:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .sec-bar { width: 4px; height: 24px; background: var(--gold); border-radius: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .sec-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .sec-rule { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--rule); }

  /* ── CARDS GRID ── */
  .cards-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  .cards-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  @media(max-width: 700px) {
    .cards-3, .cards-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 16px;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--slate);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .stat-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .stat-card-val { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--ink); }
  .stat-card-lab { font-size: 11px; color: var(--steel); margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 400; }
  .stat-card.accent { border-top-color: var(--gold); }
  .stat-card.accent .stat-card-val { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── SCORE METER ── */
  .score-wrap {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .score-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .score-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--steel); width: 90px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .score-bar-bg {
    flex: 1;
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--panel);
    border-radius: 99px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .score-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 99px;
    transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
  }
  .score-pct { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; width: 40px; text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ── DIFF / AREA BADGES ── */
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  .badge.high   { background: var(--diff-high-bg); color: var(--diff-high); }
  .badge.mid    { background: var(--diff-mid-bg);  color: var(--diff-mid); }
  .badge.low    { background: var(--diff-low-bg);  color: var(--diff-low); }
  .badge.dialogue { background: rgba(74,111,165,0.12); color: var(--area-dialogue); }
  .badge.text     { background: rgba(92,138,110,0.12); color: var(--area-text); }
  .badge.vocab    { background: rgba(142,111,163,0.12); color: var(--area-vocab); }
  .badge.grammar  { background: rgba(176,125,82,0.12); color: var(--area-grammar); }
  .badge.written  { background: rgba(106,143,160,0.12); color: var(--area-written); }

  /* ── CHART GRID ── */
  .chart-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  @media(max-width:700px) { .chart-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .chart-box {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 20px 18px;
  }
  .chart-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--slate);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--panel);
  }

  /* Bar chart */
  .bar-chart { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .bar-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--steel); width: 72px; flex-shrink: 0; text-align: right; }
  .bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 22px; background: var(--panel); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-right: 8px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: white;
    transition: width 1.4s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
    min-width: 32px;
  }
  .bar-count { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; width: 30px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Donut chart */
  .donut-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .donut-svg { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .donut-legend { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .donut-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .donut-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .donut-item-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--steel); }
  .donut-item-val   { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-left: auto; padding-left: 12px; }

  /* ── QUESTION TABLE ── */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  thead tr { background: var(--ink); }
  thead th {
    padding: 12px 10px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  thead th:first-child { border-radius: 12px 0 0 0; padding-left: 16px; }
  thead th:last-child  { border-radius: 0 12px 0 0; }
  tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--panel); transition: background 0.15s; }
  tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  tbody tr:hover { background: var(--cream); }
  tbody tr.written-row { background: #FAFAF6; }
  tbody tr.wrong-row { background: #FFF8F8; }
  tbody tr.partial-row { background: #FFFCF5; }
  td {
    padding: 10px 10px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--panel);
  }
  td:first-child { padding-left: 16px; }
  .num-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 32px; height: 24px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    background: var(--slate);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }
  .num-badge.written { background: var(--area-written); }
  .stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: -1px; }
  .result-ok   { color: #3A6B50; font-size: 16px; }
  .result-fail { color: #8C4A4A; font-size: 16px; }
  .result-part { color: #7A6830; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
  .point-text  { color: var(--slate); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* ── POINT CARDS ── */
  .point-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .point-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--slate);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .point-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); transform: translateX(2px); }
  .point-rank {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900;
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: white;
  }
  .point-body { flex: 1; }
  .point-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .point-desc  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--steel); line-height: 1.55; }
  .code {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--panel);
    color: var(--slate);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin: 1px;
  }

  /* ── STRATEGY ── */
  .strategy-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  @media(max-width:700px) { .strategy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .strategy-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .strategy-head {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .strategy-body { padding: 16px 18px; }
  .strategy-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--panel);
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .strategy-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .strategy-item-icon {
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .strategy-item-text { color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.5; }
  .strategy-item-text strong { color: var(--ink); }

  /* ── WEAK ── */
  .weak-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .weak-item {
    background: var(--diff-high-bg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(140,74,74,0.15);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--diff-high);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .weak-num { font-weight: 900; color: var(--diff-high); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .weak-text { color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .site-footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .footer-logo { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .footer-sub  { font-size: 11px; color: #5A7A95; }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
  .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── DIFF METER ── */
  .diff-meter {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .diff-big-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); width: 80px; }
  .diff-stars-big { font-size: 24px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .diff-tag {
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--diff-mid);
    background: var(--diff-mid-bg);
  }
  .diff-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--steel); flex: 1; min-width: 200px; line-height: 1.55; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── HEADER ── -->
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="site-header-inner">
    <div class="logo">
      <span class="logo-main">영어쑥쑥어학원</span>
      <span class="logo-sub">ENGLISH SSUKSSUK ACADEMY</span>
    </div>
    <span class="header-badge">학교 시험 분석 리포트</span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-tag">2026학년도 1학기 중간고사</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title"><span>부곡중학교</span> 3학년 영어</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">2026년 4월 29일 실시 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 과목코드 (12) &nbsp;·&nbsp; 2교시</p>
    <div class="hero-cards">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <span class="hero-card-val">28</span>
        <div class="hero-card-lab">총 문항</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card">
        <span class="hero-card-val">100</span>
        <div class="hero-card-lab">총 배점</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card">
        <span class="hero-card-val">60</span>
        <div class="hero-card-lab">객관식 배점</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card">
        <span class="hero-card-val">40</span>
        <div class="hero-card-lab">서·논술형 배점</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card">
        <span class="hero-card-val gold">90</span>
        <div class="hero-card-lab">학생 예상 점수</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<main class="main">

  <!-- ── 학생 성취 현황 ── -->
  <div class="sec-head fade-in">
    <div class="sec-bar"></div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">📊 학생 성취 현황</h2>
    <div class="sec-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cards-4 fade-in" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-val">100%</div>
      <div class="stat-card-lab">객관식 2점 문항 (4문)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-val">100%</div>
      <div class="stat-card-lab">객관식 3점 문항 (7문)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-val">88%</div>
      <div class="stat-card-lab">객관식 4점 문항 (9문)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card accent">
      <div class="stat-card-val">88%</div>
      <div class="stat-card-lab">서·논술형 (8문항, 40점)</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="score-wrap fade-in">
    <div class="score-row">
      <span class="score-label">객관식</span>
      <div class="score-bar-bg"><div class="score-bar-fill" style="width:91.7%;background:var(--area-dialogue);">55점</div></div>
      <span class="score-pct" style="color:var(--area-dialogue);">55/60</span>
    </div>
    <div class="score-row">
      <span class="score-label">서·논술형</span>
      <div class="score-bar-bg"><div class="score-bar-fill" style="width:87.5%;background:var(--area-written);">35점</div></div>
      <span class="score-pct" style="color:var(--area-written);">35/40</span>
    </div>
    <div class="score-row" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <span class="score-label" style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);">총점</span>
      <div class="score-bar-bg"><div class="score-bar-fill" style="width:90%;background:var(--slate);">90점</div></div>
      <span class="score-pct" style="color:var(--slate);">90/100</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 종합 난이도 ── -->
  <div class="diff-meter fade-in" style="margin-top:14px;">
    <span class="diff-big-label">종합 난이도</span>
    <span class="diff-stars-big">★★★★☆</span>
    <span class="diff-tag">중상 (4/5)</span>
    <p class="diff-desc">서·논술형 비중이 40점으로 높고, to부정사·간접의문문·사역동사 등 주요 문법을 복합적으로 테스트하는 구성입니다. 객관식은 평이하나 서답형 조건 작문에서 점수 변별이 큽니다.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 출제 분석 차트 ── -->
  <div class="sec-head fade-in">
    <div class="sec-bar"></div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">📈 출제 분석</h2>
    <div class="sec-rule"></div>
